      <h2>Make a Reservation</h2>
      <p class="lead">Tables are going fast act quickly to reserve a table for you and your friends and choose which games you want to book.</p>
    </div>
    <ul class="portfolio-filter text-center">
      <h2> Select your reservation needs</h2>
      <li><a class="btn btn-default active" href="#" data-filter="*">All</a></li>
      <li><a class="btn btn-default" href="#" data-filter=".web">Single Booking</a></li>
